name: ExtendScript Included Script File
summary: Learn about .JSXINC files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: Technically JSXINC files are the same as JSX files. However, as a convention, programmers should use the ".jsxinc" extension for ExtendScript include files.
NOTE: Since ExtendScript supports additional functionality that JavaScript does not, JSXINC files are not necessarily JavaScript files.
